00:49:28.420 --> 00:49:33.840
basically as little as possible. Maybe that file and anything that's affected by it, et cetera,

00:49:33.850 --> 00:49:40.960
et cetera. So to just sit in a terminal and check the types of a program is one problem.

00:49:41.530 --> 00:49:46.300
