00:50:29.620 --> 00:50:34.380
like a lot of how we approached the design. And we spent a lot of time trying to get that right

00:50:34.380 --> 00:50:39.420
and give us like a good foundation for building that. So does it do progressive stuff if there's

00:50:39.500 --> 00:50:45.080
like some huge code base and some, it makes some changes. Will it try to give you answers sooner

