00:54:13.960 --> 00:54:20.140
just change one part of one file, Salsa can just flow that change through the graph of queries,

00:54:20.770 --> 00:54:25.940
and figure out exactly which queries may have been affected and need to re-execute, and all the others

00:54:25.950 --> 00:54:32.460
can just be left alone. So it allows us to kind of have that level of very fine-grained incrementality

00:54:32.480 --> 00:54:36.100
